{"tid":1541861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，無真普選咩都唔使講呀","createTime":"2019-09-04T16:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T14:32:31.000Z","uid":189587,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e2699ec98fe838bd55d70282bfc786a5226c7e","tid":1541861,"uid":189587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:28:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tU3ZrI037wc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtU3ZrI037wc&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJFUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=1616551c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tU3ZrI037wc</a><br />\n<br />\n有手足之前整左呢條片講<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不論咩形式既調查</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都係無撚用！<br />\n都係無撚用！<br />\n都係無撚用！</span></span><br />\n（大部分人唔鍾意睇字，推爆條片去）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04oFhX7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04oFhX7.jpg&h=d921aa8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔離個post都講左啦，<br />\n四餸一湯，<br />\n要一齊上，<br />\n宜家只係上個湯，<br />\n仲要凍哂，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你啦！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柒婆今日以<span style=\"color: purple;\">「特別監警調查委員會」</span>取替<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「獨立調查委員會」</strong></span>，<br />\n但新加入個兩條友又係蛇鼠一窩：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">余林青萍</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">選特首果陣，係777競選辦資深顧問</span><br />\n（詳情請睇另一個post：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1539786/page/1）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1539786/page/1）</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林定國</span></strong>[/size=4]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">在任大律師公會主席，沒有反對一地兩檢，上年曾經講過唔排除做律政司（恨到出哂面咁）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PtNyCBp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPtNyCBp.jpg&h=7d7c677d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做嚟都哂氣，一句到尾，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無雙真選</strong></span><br />\n柒婆自high的委員會也好<br />\n獨立調查委員會也好<br />\n<strong>[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">都不能制裁班狗！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9fdd782bd8d4e4e081a580fe677f6352021df159","tid":1541861,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efbae50d1d47cdfe493ffcc91e9ceb59bc2c1be9","tid":1541861,"uid":258462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"中共最叻邊打邊談，到人權法有消息，就放風展開獨立調查委員會，到時就真係大鑊，呢個會即刻降唔少溫。<br />\n<br />\n今日田北辰都有講話要展開獨立調查委員會，可能其實果五大訴求已經成為中美bargain嘅籌碼<br />\n<br />\n唔可以比啲鬼佬覺得我地贏咗！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求只有真普選解決到香港問題，因為真普選能喺香港注入不可逆嘅民主元素入政制，令香港擺脫中央控制。<br />\n<br />\n依個訴求喺無可能實現，因為中央唔會比你咁做。所有嘢要繼續，直到人權法立到，香港人先可以鬆口氣，否則香港人好快被滅族！<br />\n<br />\n國際輿論比個最無用嘅訴求打擊得好嚴重！"},{"pid":"782034424f6dd2a2c1018d7a4ed396d591c2a195","tid":1541861,"uid":189587,"lik